br />\nFat %: The percentage of total body weight that is fat.<br />\n<br />\nFat Mass: Total weight of fat mass in the body.<br />\n<br />\nFFM: Fat Free Mass is comprised of muscle, bone, tissue, water, and all other fat free mass in the body.<br />\n<br />\nTBW: Total Body Water is the amount of water retained in the body. TBW is said to comprise between 50%-70% of total body weight. Generally, men tend to have higher water weight than woman due to a greater amount of muscle. <br />\n<br />\nDesirable Range: Healthy range for Fat % and Fat Mass. This range is printed only when standard mode is selected."},{"pid":"ecb2fe85780f7fb90899133d0bf704abd0052852","tid":1190951,"uid":143456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"662aeb8b1bce8dbe386c0d63e80ba8e4df9d4bfb","tid":1190951,"uid":85543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:55:47.000Z","msg":"你個test都幾廢<br />\n無muscle mass"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"即係淨低嘅係骨重同水？"},{"pid":"8e668c2822fd5ecef53c75be640be1defd34adc4","tid":1190951,"uid":85543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb2fe85780f7fb90899133d0bf704abd0052852","tid":1190951,"uid":143456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"662aeb8b1bce8dbe386c0d63e80ba8e4df9d4bfb","tid":1190951,"uid":85543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:55:47.000Z","msg":"你個test都幾廢<br />\n無muscle mass"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"即係淨低嘅係骨重同水？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"FFM: Fat Free Mass is comprised of muscle, bone, tissue, water, and all other fat free mass in the body.<br />\n<br />\nFFM = 體重-體脂肪重"},{"pid":"25da916deba45c79963d394d0e563f9b76eb7274","tid":1190951,"uid":143456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e668c2822fd5ecef53c75be640be1defd34adc4","tid":1190951,"uid":85543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb2fe85780f7fb90899133d0bf704abd0052852","tid":1190951,"uid":1434